# Conda Environment

This project uses the conda environment **GenAI**.

- Activate before running Python/backend commands: `conda activate GenAI`
- When suggesting terminal commands for this project, assume or include activation of the GenAI environment
- For pip installs, backend runs, or Python scripts, use the GenAI environment
